<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Phone Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }

    .header img {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666666;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .content a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

     .verification-code {
      font-size: 32px;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999999;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1499988921418-b7df40ff03f9?ixlib=rb-4.0.3" alt="Company Logo">
      <h1>Verify Your Phone</h1>
    </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your phone verification code is:</p>
    <div class="verification-code">{{code}}</div>
    <p>This code will expire in 5 minutes. Please enter this code in the app to verify your phone number.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this verification code, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thanks,<br>The Naushad LLC Team</p>
  </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Naushad LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>